author: @ossiren
content: Such a beautiful soul, not because I say so or her other fans say so, but because she has proven it time and time again. She has always been an ally, a supporter, an activist. She birthed, adopted and raised beautiful children who are now amazing people just like her and her people talk crap when they have done nothing to help humanity. This is a queen.
